      "expand": false,
      "html": "<blockquote style=\"border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8ex; padding-left: 1ex;\"><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Hello, wanted to let you know that we will not be able to attend this weekend. My mom fell and broke her arm and will have to take care of her. Also, my daughter's fiancé got mandated to work this  weekend. </span></div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">So sorry </span></div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Monica</span></div><div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\"><br><br></span></div><div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">null</span></div></div></div><div><div><br></div><div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">On Mon, Apr 27, 2026 at 5:39 PM Andre Raw &lt;</span><a href=\"mailto:team@comeketocatering.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\"><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">team@comeketocatering.com</span></a><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">&gt; wrote:</span></div><blockquote style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8ex; border-left: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); padding-left: 1ex;\"><div><strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Hi Monica,</span></strong></div><div><br></div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">The countdown is on! 🎉 We can’t wait to see you </span><strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Sunday May 17</span></strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\"> for an incredible tasting experience. Get ready to enjoy a variety of delicious dishes, meet our team, and start bringing your event vision to life!<br></span></div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">📍 </span><strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Location:</span></strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\"> 199 Main St., Fitchburg, MA 01420<br>⏰ </span><strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Arrival Time:</span></strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\"> 2:00 PM </span><strong><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Please arrive 15 minutes earlier!</span></strong></div><div><br></div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Come hungry and ready to enjoy! If you have any last-minute questions, feel free to reach out. We can’t wait to see you there! 😃🔥</span></div><div><span data-system-generated=\"quote\"><img src=\"cid:ii_19df59f594dea654a7f1\" alt=\"image.png\" style=\"width: 852px; max-width: 100%;\"></span></div><div><br></div><div dir=\"ltr\"><div style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34);\"><div style='margin: 8px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div dir=\"ltr\" style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div dir=\"ltr\" style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div dir=\"ltr\" style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><span style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><span data-system-generated=\"quote\"><br><br><br><br>-----<br>Regards,</span></span></div></div><div style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><div style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><strong><span style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><span data-system-generated=\"quote\">Andre Raw</span></span></strong></div><div><br></div><div><em><span style='font-family: \"Google Sans\", Roboto, RobotoDraft, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;'><span dat